there is an infinity of ways of living

274
00:10:35,119 --> 00:10:36,340
or at least

275
00:10:36,340 --> 00:10:39,351
six main groups which are divided into two classes

276
00:10:39,451 --> 00:10:41,411
thaht we will present you now.

